">&quot;Among the Jews are some who, like Saul of Tarsus, are mighty in the </div><div class="t m4b5 x3b h29 yaec ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Scriptures, and these will proclaim with wonderful power the immutability </div><div class="t m24a x3b h29 yaed ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the law of God. The God of Israel will bring this to pass in our day. His </div><div class="t m27c x3b h29 yaee ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">arm is not shortened that it cannot save. As His servants labor in faith for </div><div class="t m62 x3b h29 yaef ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">those who have long been neglected and despised, His salvation will be re-</div><div class="t m159 x3b h29 yaf0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">vealed.&quot;â€”The </div><div class="t m3cf x75 h29 yaf0 ff7 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Acts of the Apostles, </div><div class="t m124 xbe h29 yac2 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 380, 381. </div><div class="t m2c2 x3b h24 yaf1 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FURTHER STUDY AND MEDITATION: </div><div class="t m3fe x8c h29 yda ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Read </div><div class="t mce xa5 h29 y43e ff7 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Acts of the Apos-</div><div class="t m44f x3b h29 yaf2 ff7 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tles, </div><div class="t m3b5 x7 h29 yaf3 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Salvation to the Jews,&quot; pp. 372-382. </div><div class="t m450 x3b h29 yaf4 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: Although Israel&apos;s rejection of the Messiah resulted in the </div><div class="t m4f3 x3b h29 yaf5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">loss of their status as a chosen nation before God, the Lord seeks to lead </div><div class="t m423 x3b h29 yaf6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Jewish people to salvation through Jesus Christ. Those who believe are </div><div class="t m3c4 x3b h29 yaf7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">united with believing Gentiles into one body as spiritual Israel. </div><div class="t m1de x59 h24 yaf8 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">76 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000